<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sceptical-adj">sceptical <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'skeptɪkl/    美 /'skeptɪkl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(持)怀疑态度的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He denied taking money but we were sceptical.
他否认收了钱，但我们对此表示怀疑。</p><footer>人教⑤ – 4</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-sceptical-about-of">(be) sceptical about / of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>对…持怀疑态度：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She is sceptical of everything.
她怀疑一切。</p></div></div>